sequenceDiagram
    title Ticket Purchase Hold and Confirm (Happy Path)
    autonumber
    participant Client as API Client
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant Purchase as Ticket Purchase Orchestrator
    participant SeatInv as Seat Inventory Service (gRPC)
    participant Credit as Credit Service
    participant Ticket as Ticket Service

    Client->>Gateway: POST /purchase/hold/{inventoryId}
    Gateway->>Purchase: Forward authenticated request
    Purchase->>SeatInv: HoldSeat(inventory_id, user_id, ttl)
    SeatInv-->>Purchase: success + hold_token + held_until
    Purchase-->>Gateway: 200 held
    Gateway-->>Client: holdToken + heldUntil

    Client->>Gateway: POST /purchase/confirm/{inventoryId}
    Gateway->>Purchase: Forward authenticated request
    Purchase->>SeatInv: GetSeatStatus(inventory_id)
    SeatInv-->>Purchase: held by user + token valid
    Purchase->>Credit: Verify credits
    Credit-->>Purchase: sufficient balance
    Purchase->>SeatInv: SellSeat(inventory_id, hold_token)
    SeatInv-->>Purchase: sold
    Purchase->>Ticket: Create ticket record
    Ticket-->>Purchase: ticketId
    Purchase->>Credit: Deduct credits
    Credit-->>Purchase: success
    Purchase-->>Gateway: 201 purchase confirmed
    Gateway-->>Client: ticket + transaction details

sequenceDiagram
    title Transfer OTP Verification (Seller Path)
    autonumber
    participant Buyer as Buyer
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant TransferOrch as Transfer Orchestrator
    participant TransferSvc as Transfer Service
    participant OTP as OTP Wrapper

    Buyer->>Gateway: POST /transfer/{id}/buyer-verify
    Gateway->>TransferOrch: Forward JWT-authenticated request
    TransferOrch->>TransferSvc: PATCH status + buyerOtpVerified=true
    TransferSvc-->>TransferOrch: pending_seller_otp
    TransferOrch->>OTP: Send seller OTP
    OTP-->>TransferOrch: sellerVerificationSid
    TransferOrch->>TransferSvc: PATCH sellerVerificationSid
    TransferSvc-->>TransferOrch: updated transfer
    TransferOrch-->>Gateway: 200 buyer verified
    Gateway-->>Buyer: seller OTP initiated
